                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d55">
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Mr. <persName type="from">Wharton</persName> to Mr. <persName
                            type="to">Mizner</persName>
                    </hi>.</head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Department of State</hi>,<lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1890-08-07">
                            <hi rend="italic">August</hi> 7, 1890</date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>Mr. Wharton informs Mr. Mizner that General Guirala has telegraphed that messages
                    from the Department to Mr. Mizner are not detained in Salvador. Mr. Wharton adds
                    that the detention would appear to be in Guatemalan territory, and instructs Mr.
                    Mizner to be watchful in that direction.</p>
            </div>
